Adedeji Adeleke (a mụrụ n'ụbọchị nke ise n'ọnwa atọ, n'afọ 1957) bụ onye Naijiria, onye ọchụnta ego, onye isi oche nke Mahadum Adeleke Ọ bụkwa onye isi oche nke Pacific Holdings Limited.  Davido, onye egwu Naịjirịa na Sharon Adeleke. Ọ lụrụ Dr Vero Adeleke onye nwụrụ na abalị ise na onwa Machị, na afọ 2003.
